ure><p></p><p><strong>凤翔海洋</strong>（Hololive附属​​）有290万观众，<strong>拉普拉斯黑暗</strong>（同上）有110万观众，<strong>艾玛·相泽</strong><strong>（</strong> Buispo！）/伊卡·加尤（独立）/<strong>千草西园</strong>（虹山寺）有50万观众， <strong>MOTHERv3</strong> （独立）有40万人， <strong>Kozakutoto</strong> （Buispo！）有20万人。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>本文介绍有关 VTuber 人才的信息以及每个机构、团体和公司的官方 YouTube 频道的订阅者数量。<strong>请注意，这些数据并不代表行业中每个人才、机构、团体或公司的规模或份额。</strong></p><p><em>根据 ANYCOLOR 使用受版权保护的材料的要求，本网站将从 2021 年 8 月起停止引用与 VTuber 团体“Nijisanji”和“NIJISANJI EN（New）”相关的图像。</em></p></blockquote><p></p><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1"> 290万人</h2><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1_1">宝生海洋</h3><figure class="wp-block-image"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="97985" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-is-the-first-active-japanese-vtuber-to-reach-2-5-million-youtube-subscribers/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/houshou_marine_youtube_channel_30_july_2023.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp