</style><p>截至12月3日，OWOZU已确认9名VTuber艺人的加盟，随着这位新艺人的登场，预计加盟的VTuber艺人数量将增至12人。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp-vtuber wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp-vtuber"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="KUiAnYYTDV"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/owozu-vtuber-rakkun-takes-a-month-hiatus-due-to-throat-surgery/">OWOZU 旗下 VTuber Rakkun 因喉咙手术中断一个月</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“OWOZU所属VTuber Rakkun因咽喉手术将暂停活动1个月” — P2y.jp - VTuber最新消息" src="https://p2y.jp/owozu-vtuber-rakkun-takes-a-month-hiatus-due-to-throat-surgery/embed/#?secret=OnHUORr80T#?secret=KUiAnYYTDV" data-secret="KUiAnYYTDV" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp-vtuber wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp-vtuber"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Q8BlD4r0Ka"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/latin-american-vtuber-agency-owozu-has-risen-to-2nd-place-in-the-world-in-average-number-of-youtube-subscribers-per-talents/">拉丁美洲 VTuber 机构 OWOZU 的人均频道订阅人数已上升至全球第二位</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“拉丁美洲的 VTuber 机构 OWOZU 的人均频道订阅人数已上升至全球第二位” — P2y.jp - VTuber 最新消息" src="https://p2y.jp/latin-american-vtuber-agency-owozu-has-risen-to-2nd-place-in-the-world-in-average-number-of-youtube-subscribers-per-talents/embed/#?secret=Q675IHaWxi#?secret=Q8BlD4r0Ka" data-secret="Q8BlD4r0Ka" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.owozu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="奥沃祖">奥沃祖</a></p><cite>官方网站</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-b